Hourly water quality by site

Source: R/data.R
wq_hourly.Rd

High-frequency water-quality time series collected from in-situ sensors.

Usage

data(wq_hourly)

Format

A tibble/data frame with N rows and 6 variables:

date_time

POSIXct. Timestamp in local time or UTC (state which one).

site

chr. Site identifier (e.g., "XYZ").

sensor

chr. Sensor identifier or type.

cond_uScm

dbl. Specific conductivity (µS/cm).

do_mgL

dbl. Dissolved oxygen (mg/L).

turb_FNU

dbl. Turbidity (FNU).

Source

NEON products (list product codes + your processing steps).
